ygData.messageBody:
i know there are SoW boots in Najena, but they are a rather difficult find
(one of the three mages at the end of Najena has them sometimes). i know
what you mean about how good it would be for solo. this weekend i had to
tank a young kodiak at 1/2 hp and i had no mana. nice to know i can do it
if i have to, but i barely won. i was almost toast by the time he turned
tail and tried to get away!

belphenor
